# Data Science For Healthcare Nitin Singh — Passos Operacionais

Conteudo extraido do livro 'Data Science For Healthcare Nitin Singh'. Contem passos, tecnicas e principios baseados na obra original.

## 1. Conceitos Fundamentais
- Data Science for Healthcare Acknowledgement This book came together with help from many people.
- I am grateful for the time, patience, and honest feedback that carried it to the finish line.
- Thank you to the BPB editorial team for backing the idea and guiding it from proposal to manuscript.
